---
title: Ultimate Fish and Chips with broccoli and parsley lemon mayo
description: Give the chipper a miss tonight and make your own at home instead. The decadent golden baked fish fillet and twice cooked chips in this recipe are balanced with a healthy helping of broccoli for added crunch.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF220921_R11_W46_IE_IEXCFCLF0008-1_KB_Main_high-199ccdc7.jpg
